<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Social_information_seeking&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: External links"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>People associated with social information seeking include:
</p>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mathcs.emory.edu/~eugene/">Eugene Agichtein</a></li>
